  "about": "Age: 15 (past) 27 (present) 18 (current)\nBirthdate: August 20, 1990\nHeight: 162 cm\nWeight: 56 kg\nBlood type: B\nGangs: Tokyo manji gang \nManjirou Sano is a founding member and the leader of Tokyo Manji Gang.\n\nMikey is usually a carefree teenager who loves to joke and play pranks around those he considers his close friends. He cares for them greatly and is determined to protect their honor. He rarely shows any sign of weakness, as he believes himself to be the foundation and support for Toman, and if the pillar himself were to display weakness, Toman would also be weakened.\n\nAs Toman's leader, his aura changes dramatically, becoming imposing and commanding. While its members respect Mikey, they also hold a degree of fear toward him and his immense prowess. He is also concerned for Toman on an individual level, as shown when he decides to rally the entire gang to seek revenge for one of its member's friend.",
  "note": null,
  "source": "anime"
